{"tid":1762932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何柱國撰文力挺李嘉誠 直指吳秋北作不實揣測","createTime":"2019-11-30T03:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T16:04:56.000Z","uid":28765,"like":117,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"49930eb74b43ee6e12ee5b8e4c96c77f947f75b6","tid":1762932,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191130/large/1575081482_4999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191130%2Flarge%2F1575081482_4999.jpg&h=255ff6b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星島（1105）主席何柱國今日於以「我所認識的李嘉誠先生」為題，於《星島日報》撰文支持長和系資深顧問李嘉誠。<br />\n文中提到，香港近日受到社會事件影響，經濟急劇惡化，李嘉誠慷慨捐出10億元應急錢，資助受影響的中小企。但無奈這無私的行動卻受到部份人士，包括工聯會會長吳秋北的誤解，以至作出種種不實的揣測。<br />\n<br />\n何柱國指，應急錢「猶如經歷久旱後的甘霖」，滋潤了香港社會的人心，「由此可見李先生是個愛國愛港的慈祥長者」。<br />\n文中亦提到，李先生深明樹大招風的道理，近年社會上出現一些關於他的抨擊，他當以平常心面對，「要在這個時間獨善其身並不容易，何況是要站出來做應該做的事？李先生冒著承受蜚短流長的風險，堅持挺身而出解中小企於倒懸，皆因明白到愛中國、愛香港的社會領袖，有責任為社會穩定出錢出力。」<br />\n<br />\n何柱國於文末認為，李嘉誠在商界取得無人能及的成就，他心中已別無所求，「只期望香港好、國家好，這是我認識的李嘉誠先生」。<br />\n李嘉誠今年9月首度開腔，希望執政者能對社會未來主人翁「網開一面」，惹來親建制人士不滿。並中港區人大代表、工聯會會長吳秋北更在Facebook分享改圖，諷刺他是「曱甴王」。<br />\n之後李嘉誠推出應急錢，雖然大受商戶歡迎，但吳秋北卻指不清楚對方目的，認為縱容暴力後才作出修補關係的舉動，是本末倒置。<br />\n<br />\n星島今個月初公佈，正與對公司有興趣之潛在獨立投資者進行磋商，董事會強調，該磋商可能成事，亦可能不成事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191130/60326721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60326721&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY7Tr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=68c14ebb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60326721&h=b9d838a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191130/60326721</a>"},{"pid":"97ecbd6d6fb26455d4462f68a69a97e755c8e03b","tid":1762932,"uid":77092,"like":155,"dislike":1,"score":154,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:03:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b067c20bdd4ef27edbdfa80b1d0709f597af2df","tid":1762932,"uid":51840,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"風起了..."},{"pid":"dcab4a811dea075a080a3dea00470ee8c4347a10","tid":1762932,"uid":12554,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"煙仔何第幾次轉身？"},{"pid":"9f2321d313e562d883facadd42be765c004ab834","tid":1762932,"uid":53498,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"淆底？"},{"pid":"e36aa130ceb81bcc155c867581437414e6492af2","tid":1762932,"uid":187664,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:09:39.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾講野勁藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd398066afc6bb7261b5e1e922d6bef0eac3dab2","tid":1762932,"uid":248098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:10:33.000Z","msg":"走lu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa21eac1acaa87d7062972ccec660371f95b5eff","tid":1762932,"uid":190101,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:11:15.000Z","msg":"因為人權法啦，條仆街大把資產係美國"},{"pid":"6839393ce4cda7abae8b561b58a91b7857deb486","tid":1762932,"uid":21483,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:11:57.000Z","msg":"佢收到風自己俾人制裁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6bac35ff9ac2d53256b891ae7a58533c19306d","tid":1762932,"uid":217679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:12:24.000Z","msg":"食屎啦炒河，你正一屎忽鬼，影衰你阿爺呀"},{"pid":"a85c7c7a576be9febd3a277010617ce76974300d","tid":1762932,"uid":37524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"aa21eac1acaa87d7062972ccec660371f95b5eff","tid":1762932,"uid":190101,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:11:15.000Z","msg":"因為人權法啦，條仆街大把資產係美國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"