nance/realtime/article/20191130/60326721</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:31:41.000Z","msg":"依條撚樣<br />\n你認為你走得luck?"},{"pid":"9e886ccc6b75a5fe7380c6f94b16808eff707df1","tid":1762932,"uid":55386,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"我欣賞自由黨果班商人  雖然建制 但貫徹始終<br />\n<br />\n但狗柱國呢D牆頭草 你能夠發到達都係因為你搭緊香港起飛班機<br />\n比你依家先創業唔L比蝗玩死?"},{"pid":"6c0d899abfa93e1c162dcccad09ee1a880d8fff5","tid":1762932,"uid":86628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:36:46.000Z","msg":"煙仔何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1349f067c44574ef8bc6348c3a4fda6e85282a","tid":1762932,"uid":47239,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9e886ccc6b75a5fe7380c6f94b16808eff707df1","tid":1762932,"uid":55386,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"我欣賞自由黨果班商人  雖然建制 但貫徹始終<br />\n<br />\n但狗柱國呢D牆頭草 你能夠發到達都係因為你搭緊香港起飛班機<br />\n比你依家先創業唔L比蝗玩死?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"煙仔何靠老豆喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcb467b8be4af029f3a79579fbe962d5d703617","tid":1762932,"uid":155784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:37:47.000Z","msg":"義憤民誠仔係愛國的，係國內投資捐款好多<br />\n<br />\n但愛國不等於愛黨。佢憎共產黨想佢倒台"},{"pid":"dcf327185f0b43f0f14ebfdd2732c4b00854295f","tid":1762932,"uid":286336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:37:48.000Z","msg":"工賊會又做過乜撚嘢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905b719ef65575c6a4e0606a7636c111c1754f1c","tid":1762932,"uid":190101,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8796395cee881df31ee98e8e17f7fbb3eec6aaa5","tid":1762932,"uid":110019,"like":1,"