le.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6188394348a902ae9faabbc58d5ddea1d0ebd13d","tid":1762932,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f2321d313e562d883facadd42be765c004ab834","tid":1762932,"uid":53498,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"淆底？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:47:30.000Z","msg":"佢8成家族資產係美國"},{"pid":"cf81591fce3d70eb67d6fcb5bb687ad5436a54cb","tid":1762932,"uid":277147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:47:46.000Z","msg":"藍絲冇信念同冇腰骨唔係新聞"},{"pid":"2ee2b4ca3c6e1ef055bb32d868b2afc188f646fc","tid":1762932,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"何柱國=共狗"},{"pid":"b6c012195c8af63fe5abac4866037ae9aa44dec3","tid":1762932,"uid":63694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:54:43.000Z","msg":"心理壓力大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660cf3095defc96e115b9ae8f6466022ba6b9de1","tid":1762932,"uid":288913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49930eb74b43ee6e12ee5b8e4c96c77f947f75b6","tid":1762932,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191130/large/1575081482_4999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191130%2Flarge%2F1575081482_4999.jpg&h=255ff6b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星島（1105）主席何柱國今日於以「我所認識的李嘉誠先生」為題，於《星島日報》撰文支持長和系資深顧問李嘉誠。<br />\n文中提到，香港近日受到社會事件影響，經濟急劇惡化，李嘉誠慷慨捐出10億元應急錢，資助受影響的中小企。但無奈這無私的行動卻受到部份人士，包括工聯會會長吳秋北的誤解，以至作出種種不實的揣測。<br />\n<br />\n何柱國指，應急錢「猶如經歷久旱後的甘霖」，滋潤了香港社會的人心，「由此可見李先生是個愛國愛港的慈祥長者」。<br />\n文中亦提到，李先生深明樹大招風的道理，近年社會上出現一些關於他的抨擊，他當以平常心面對，「要在這個時間獨善其身並不容易，何況是要站出來做應該做的事？李先生冒著承受蜚短流長的風險，堅持挺身而出解中小企於倒懸，皆因明白到愛中國、愛香港的社會領袖，有責任為社會穩定出錢出力。」<br />\n<br />\n何柱國於文末認為，李嘉誠在商界取得無人能及的成就，他心中已別無所求，「只期望香港好、國家好，這是我認識的李嘉誠先生」。<br />\n李嘉誠今年9月首度開腔，希望執政者能對社會未來主人翁「網開一面」，惹來親建制人士不滿。並中港區人大代表、工聯會會長吳秋北更在Facebook分享改圖，諷刺他是「曱甴王」。<br />\n之後李嘉誠推出應急錢，雖然大受商戶歡迎，但吳秋北卻指不清楚對方目的，認為縱容暴力後才作出修補關係的舉動，是本末倒置。<br />\n<br />\n星島今個月初公佈，正與對公司有興趣之潛在獨立投資者進行磋商，董事會強調，該磋商可能成事，亦可能不成事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191130/60326721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60326721&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY7Tr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=68c14ebb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60326721&h=b9d838a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191130/60326721</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:55:31.000Z","msg":"Seems Li Kar Shing is buying Sing Dao"},{"pid":"80a8398843dcf12edc04ba9d9d064277ac52e295","tid":1762932,"uid":270619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12510546f95536dd93bc530cb697928797e90955","tid":1762932,"uid":103981,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:15:32.000Z","msg":"吳秋北呢D人學人笑誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投胎十萬次佢都唔會有人地既成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji